headline: Steelcase (SCS) Q1 Earnings and Revenues Surpass Estimates
summary: Steelcase (SCS) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +66.67% and +3.05%, respectively, for the quarter ended May 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
